\MyProject\LolitaFramework\Core\Arr::flatten
===

The Arr::flatten function will flatten a multi-dimensional array into a single level.

Example usage
---
```php

$array = ['name' => 'Joe', 'languages' => ['PHP', 'Ruby']];

$array = Arr::flatten($array);

// ['Joe', 'PHP', 'Ruby'];

```

Parameters
---
_array_  __$array__

_int_  __$depth__

Return Value
---
__array__
